".br\n"
"STUVWXYZ\n"
".sp\n"
".ps 16\n"
".vs (\\n(.s+2)p\n"
".fp 5 SHOWBOAT\n"
".ft R\n"
"To use it for the first letter of a paragraph, it will look like:\n"
